  "title": "Supervisor/Manager - F&B",
  "description": "<p><p><strong></strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Lead & Inspire:</strong> Guide, motivate, and develop a talented team. Foster a positive, supportive environment where everyone feels valued and empowered to grow.</p></li><li><p><strong>Deliver Excellence:</strong> Own the guest experience from start to finish, ensuring superb food, genuine service, and a spotless, welcoming environment.</p></li><li><p><strong>Operations:</strong> Keep daily rhythms smooth. Manage inventory, build smart schedules, and handle the logistics so the café runs seamlessly.</p></li><li><p><strong>Store:</strong> Take accountability for your location’s performance, your team’s morale, and upholding our top standards in every detail.</p></li><li><p><strong>Grow:</strong> Receive ongoing training and mentorship to fuel your career journey into broader leadership roles within our company.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>A natural, people-first leader who thrives in a fast-paced, lively setting.</p></li><li><p>A proactive problem-solver who sees a challenge as a chance to improve.</p></li><li><p>Curious, humble, and genuinely eager to learn and develop new skills.</p></li><li><p>Deeply passionate about creating warm, positive experiences that people remember.</p></li></ul></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>EA Personnel R22110043 Tan Eng Kang</p><p>EA License 21C0430 A Dreamworks Company Pte Ltd</p>",
